#

Arugula and Apple Salad

10 min
$8.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthyLight

Description

A refreshing and crunchy salad combining peppery arugula, sweet apples, and a tangy vinaigrette.

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • apple (sliced, any variety): 1 large
  • walnuts (chopped): 1/4 cup
  • feta cheese (crumbled): 1/3 cup
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • apple cider vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
